{"id": 1751, "genre": 1001, "title": "恐怖电影有哪些固定桥段，你能一眼识破？", "description": "好好好，此处应有鬼影/尖叫/第一波倒霉鬼丧生了。", "record_count": 4196, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170621174235vdkGziuwOPm7jRoy.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-22T03:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 215296, "content": "BGM变得激烈时一般不会有问题，缓和五秒大家都放松的时候…baaam！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413086}, {"id": 215297, "content": "分开行动吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 383472}, {"id": 215299, "content": "第一个恐吓大家有鬼的必先遭殃…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762205}, {"id": 215811, "content": "出现恐怖气氛音乐，之后配合下……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062646}, {"id": 215300, "content": "爱打嘴炮的人最先死", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055367}, {"id": 215812, "content": "只要背景音乐突然变了 或者突然安静了 就一定有东西要来吓你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869213}, {"id": 215301, "content": "镜头跟在主人公身后移动", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055367}, {"id": 216581, "content": "“不要吓唬自己！世界上怎么会有鬼！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065027}, {"id": 215303, "content": "感觉后面有东西，回头看没有，再转过来就……", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061349}, {"id": 215304, "content": "组团没事 分开必死", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061351}, {"id": 216328, "content": "BGM一停下来就要开始吓唬观众了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056538}, {"id": 215305, "content": "背景音乐变大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022986}, {"id": 220425, "content": "深夜在镜子面前洗脸，抬头后镜子里一般都有东西！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075428}, {"id": 230924, "content": "一般在发现动静后，往那看去，转身鬼就出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111186}, {"id": 215309, "content": "让我一个人呆一会儿！！（领盒饭）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057388}, {"id": 230925, "content": "灯光忽闪忽闪忽闪忽闪忽闪忽闪的………………然后……就不亮了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111186}, {"id": 215310, "content": "都有灯一闪一闪的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048278}, {"id": 217614, "content": "中国内地恐怖片，最后主角醒来，发现原来一切都是梦境，都是幻觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066739}, {"id": 215312, "content": "hello？is anybody here？hello～？（盒饭）", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057388}, {"id": 215313, "content": "回头（盒饭）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057388}, {"id": 215569, "content": "所有脱离队友的都会死，唯有打团才有活路，偷野偷塔落单的都得死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037202}, {"id": 215314, "content": "hey，baby，no worry！is ok！look this…ahhhhhhh～（盒饭）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057388}, {"id": 215317, "content": "转角遇到爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061331}, {"id": 215318, "content": "声音恐怖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001932}, {"id": 215831, "content": "不敢看……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057931}, {"id": 222743, "content": "你以为要吓人的时候其实什么都没有，然后肛一放松，鬼就来了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081488}, {"id": 215320, "content": "分开行动毕挂", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031498}, {"id": 215832, "content": "一片安静之后必是惊吓 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059670}, {"id": 216088, "content": "校园恐怖片一定得有怀孕堕胎被辜负", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064012}, {"id": 216089, "content": "大晚上明明感觉不对劲还偏不开灯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064012}, {"id": 215322, "content": "明明很害怕偏要继续冒险", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061375}, {"id": 220187, "content": "前方高能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074501}, {"id": 215328, "content": "明明怕到要死偏偏还好奇心大到要死", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019967}, {"id": 215584, "content": "开柜子/箱子/门，配上紧张的音乐，主角缓慢迟疑的动作，我的死穴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237054}, {"id": 221472, "content": "落单必死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077484}, {"id": 215329, "content": "对一个胆子小到看看评论都觉得怕怕的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008284}, {"id": 216865, "content": "主角到最后一刻才可能会死……主角光环", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065433}, {"id": 220193, "content": "有灯的不开灯。想开灯的没灯。\n黑长直红白群", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074566}, {"id": 215330, "content": "突然间的安静，等会儿就会出现吓你一跳的镜头orz ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061413}, {"id": 215586, "content": "地图过期-迷路-杀人狂??????", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014614}, {"id": 216866, "content": "别和单纯的小孩说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065433}, {"id": 215331, "content": "在恐怖预热的环境中，镜头只聚焦主角，之后几秒内100%会出现恐怖事件。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908059}, {"id": 215332, "content": "怕是某个人和他的配偶独深入小树林。。。响起某种怪异的风声，然后就GG了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929976}, {"id": 215844, "content": "缓慢移镜头", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001376}, {"id": 215333, "content": "知道前方有危险还一定要去搞事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567993}, {"id": 230949, "content": "回头杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110872}, {"id": 215334, "content": "进洗手间，拿出指甲刀或者修眉刀，拿美工刀之类锋利器具的下一桥段，会有恐怖的声音响起。开帘子，柜子，窗户，壁橱，会有诡异的声音。。一切都是生效在作祟。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024576}, {"id": 215335, "content": "看评论好像在看恐怖片啊。。。鸡贼惊悚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024576}, {"id": 215336, "content": "好恐怖，集思广益，收藏起来，出个专辑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024576}, {"id": 215337, "content": "角落里突然一只猫窜出来，幸亏只是猫～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061443}]}